'''詹卡洛·朱塞佩·亞歷山德羅·埃斯波西托'''（{{lang-it|Giancarlo Giuseppe Alessandro Esposito}}，{{IPA-it|dʒaŋˈkarlo dʒuˈzɛppe alesˈsandro eˈspɔːzito|pron}}，<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.loc.gov/nls/about/organization/standards-guidelines/efgh/#e |title=Say How? A Pronunciation Guide to Names of Public Figures |trans-title=怎麽說？公衆人物姓名發音指南 |website=[[國會圖書館_(美國)|美國國會圖書館]]{{link-en|國家圖書館盲人與殘障人士服務 (美國)|National Library Service for the Blind and Physically Handicapped|盲人與殘障人士服務}} |quote=Esposito, Giancarlo (jon-KÄR-lō es-pō-ZĒ-tō) |access-date={{dts|2019|8|31}} |language=en-US |archive-date=2018-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106205744/http://www.loc.gov/nls/about/organization/standards-guidelines/efgh/#e |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite AV media |title=Giancarlo Esposito Talks 'Breaking Bad' & 'Better Call Saul' |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aw-2MZdzDGY |date={{dts|2017|4|11}} |time=0:22 |location=[[悉尼|悉尼]] |work={{link-en|Studio 10}} |via=[[YouTube|YouTube]] |access-date={{dts|2019|8|31}} |language=en-AU |archive-date=2020-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609021334/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aw-2MZdzDGY |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{bd|1958年|4月26日||}}）或簡稱'''詹卡洛·埃斯波西托'''，是一位[[意大利裔美國人|意大利裔]][[美國|美國]]男演員、導演及製片人。他較知名的表現是在[[AMC_(電視頻道)|AMC]][[西部片|當代西部]][[犯罪片|犯罪]]劇集《[[絕命毒師|絕命毒師]]》第二至四季（2009–2011）中飾演[[葛斯·弗林|葛斯塔沃·「葛斯」·弗林]]一角，並因此提名[[第64屆黃金時段艾美獎|第64屆黃金時段艾美獎]]{{link-en|黃金時段艾美獎最佳劇情類劇集男配角|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Supporting Actor in a Drama Series}}。

==早期生活==
詹卡洛·埃斯波西托出生於[[丹麥|丹麥]][[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]，父親喬瓦尼·埃斯波西托（{{lang|it|Giovanni Esposito}}）是來自[[義大利|義大利]][[那不勒斯|那不勒斯]]的舞台工作人員及木匠，母親伊莉莎白·福斯特（{{lang|en|Elizabeth Foster}}）則是來自美國[[阿拉巴馬州|阿拉巴馬州]]的[[非裔美國人|非裔]]歌廳、夜店歌手。<ref>{{cite book|title=Feeling Italian: The Art of Ethnicity in America |url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=Te8TCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA174&lpg=PA174&dq=Giovanni+Esposito+Elizabeth+Foster |last=Ferraro |first=Thomas J. |publisher={{link-en|紐約大學出版社|New York University Press}} |date=2005 |page=174 |ISBN=978-0-8147-2730-0 |access-date={{dts|2019|8|31}} |language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=LeVasseur |first=Andrea |url=http://www.starpulse.com/Actors/Esposito,_Giancarlo/Biography/ |title=Giancarlo Esposito Pictures, Biography, Filmography, News, Videos |work=[[All_Movie_Guide|All Movie Guide]] |publisher=Starpulse |year=2003 |access-date={{dts|2009|04|10}} |dead-url=yes |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100121182457/http://www.starpulse.com/Actors/Esposito,_Giancarlo/Biography/ |archive-date=2010-01-21 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/64/Giancarlo-Esposito.html |title=Giancarlo Esposito Biography (1958–) |website=Film Reference |publisher=NetIndustries |quote=Giancarlo Giuseppi Alessandro Esposito; born April 26, 1958, in Copenhagen, Denmark; raised in New York, NY; father, a stagehand and carpenter; mother, an opera and nightclub singer; married Joy McManigal (a producer), June 1995; children: Shayne Lyra, Kale Lyn |access-date={{dts|2019|8|31}} |language=en |archive-date=2007-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070929111108/http://www.filmreference.com/film/64/Giancarlo-Esposito.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Giancarlo Esposito and confrontation |url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-dotheright-giancarlo-esposito_kjp6tinc,0,5112312.photo |work=[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]] |dead-url=yes |access-date=2016-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012080618/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/news/la-dotheright-giancarlo-esposito_kjp6tinc,0,5112312.photo |archive-date=2013-10-12 }}</ref>

埃斯波西托6歲時隨家人從[[歐洲|歐洲]]移居至[[紐約|紐約]][[曼哈頓|曼哈頓]]，隨後於當地[[羅馬天主教會|羅馬天主教會]][[短期大學|兩年制]]{{link-en|伊莉莎白·西頓學院|Elizabeth Seton College}}讀取廣播電視傳播學位。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Giancarlo Esposito Heads To Reggae Film Festival |url=http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20120326/ent/ent1.html |website={{link-en|Jamaica-Gleaner}} |date={{dts|2012|3|26}} |access-date={{dts|2019|8|31}} |language=en-US |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123052126/http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20120326/ent/ent1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
